Elbit Imaging Unit Gets $30 Million Loan From Eastgate Property

-- B y   S u s a n   L e r n e r
-- 
2011-09-25T07:39:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-25/elbit-imaging-unit-gets-30-million-loan-from-eastgate-property.html
Elbit Imaging Ltd. (EMIT)  said its Elbit
USA LLC unit borrowed $30 million from Eastgate Property LLC,
according to a statement filed today with the Tel Aviv Stock
Exchange.  To contact the reporter on this story:
